organization	"Answer the instance of ClassOrganizer that represents the organization 	of the messages of the receiver."	self basicOrganization ifNil:		[self organization: (ClassOrganizer defaultList: self selectors asArray sort)].	"Making sure that subject is set correctly. It should not be necessary."	self basicOrganization ifNotNil: [self basicOrganization setSubject: self].	^ self basicOrganization.